<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-2')">2</a>. An imaginary planet in ancient China, which is the counterpart of Jupiter but moves in the opposite direction.</div>
